$interpreted: Drill Sergeant: Assuming our men are trapped in a valley and surrounded, how do we break out? Jia-Shen...give us an answer.
Humpty: Turtle trash, are you deaf or are you just a bumbling turd? Didn't you hear what the Sergeant said?
Jia-Shen: ...*clears throat*...actually, the correct classification is "tortoise", I just happen to look a whole lot like a turtle.
Drill Sergeant: Everyone, shut up! I don't give a rat's behind if you're a turtle or a tortoise, give me a damn answer!
Jia-Shen: Okie dokie~based on my observations, first I'd pretend to surrender, then...
Jia-Shen: ——when the enemy puts down their guard, I'd skedaddle outta there like a bat outta hell.
Drill Sergeant: Flee? Do you have no shame!?
Jia-Shen: The Sergeant is mistaken, sir. That's called givin' one step to gain ten.
Drill Sergeant: You little...! Why wouldn't you grab ahold of this opportunity to annihilate them in one fell swoop?
Jia-Shen: Sir, first you say I oughta be ashamed, now you want me to take advantage of people. Isn't that a bit of a contradiction?
Drill Sergeant: YOU WANNA RUN! FINE! We'll see how fast you can run! Take these maps. Pop quiz! The topic? Run your goddamn butts off!
Student: Aw man! It's all the turtle's fault!
Humpty: Here you go.
Jia-Shen: Thanks, thanks.
Drill Sergeant: The route is on the map I just gave you. Don't run astray!
Drill Sergeant: Ready~GO!
Jia-Shen: (Everyone's running so fast, can't even see the darn lizard's tail...*sigh*...the Lord chooses who's at the top o' the food chain.)
Jia-Shen: (Gosh darnit, bottom feeding creatures like me...guess I gotta pull an ol' trickeroo. As long as I get my degree, that's all that matters.)
Jia-Shen: Eh? Where'd everyone go?
Drill Sergeant: Jia-Shen!? No fricking way, YOU got here first?
Jia-Shen: ME!? First place?
Student: Jia-Shen's the winner? No way, he's a goddamn turtle!
Brown Noser: Humpty didn't get first place?
Jia-Shen: (Could it be, this is my chance to shine!?)
Drill Sergeant: ...It appears...I've underestimated you this whole time, Jia-Shen.
Brown Noser: Hey Humpty, you wanna teach that smug good for nothing a lesson?
Humpty: Just wait. He won't be arrogant for long.
Student: Giant scorpions! Help~~
Drill Sergeant: What the...!? They shouldn't be out scouting for nests! Not at this time of the year!
Drill Sergeant: In any case, there's no way you got first place without cheating!
Drill Sergeant: You think you can cheat and get away with it? I know you went off track...now head to where those nasty bugs are active and attract their attention!
Jia-Shen: What!? I didn't cheat!
Drill Sergeant: The proof's right here and you wanna argue!? Never thought students from the East Alliance had such low standards!
Drill Sergeant: Now get the hell off this campus!
Jia-Shen: I...this...there must be some mistake...
Drill Sergeant: SCRAM!
Student: Never thought he would stoop that low. I mean, yeah, he looks weird, but geez, what a terrible person.
Brown Noser: Humpty, dude you're so awesome.
Humpty: This school's for nobles. No room for country trash like that.
